  "type": "npc",
  "status": "active",
  "description": "Stairwarden of the Long Stair; the Synod's pragmatic edge.",
  "narrative": "Ossuin, one name, given at her first descent forty years ago. Ulvane has been deeper than anyone living and does not talk about it - but she has heard the nursery lights sing, and unlike the Synod she thinks the living should be told before the wax runs out. VOICE: short sentences, long silences, no metaphors (Ossuin are never being metaphorical). GM ARC: the door into the Deepway. She will defy the Synod exactly once, for people who have carried a body down properly. The un-buried dead crisis is her breaking point.",
